Manual iteration-14 strict hypoxia curation ledger created from the approved iter-14 S0 expansion task, NCBI GEO ESearch/ESummary queries for hypoxia RNA-seq candidates, GEO supplementary FTP listings, direct downloads of GSE167956 workbooks and series matrix metadata, pandas workbook inspection, sha256sum of staged files under data/deg/raw/iter14, and review of MDPI article 10.3390/ijms23137262. No row was activated because inspected candidates lacked full/near-full as-published or GEO-deposited contrast-level DEG tables with gene, effect, and p/FDR fields, or failed existing replicate/gene-universe constraints.
